tourBios.curYrHigh: Rookie earned exempt status after finishing T16 at PGA TOUR Canada Qualifying School in California.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Three-year letterwinner at Utah State finished second at WAC Championships in 2007.
tourBios.personal: Favorite athlete is Fred Couples...Bucket list includes traveling the world...Enjoys 1980s movies. Motto is "The only breaks in life are the ones you earn."...Favorite course is Birch Creek GC in Smithfield, Utah, where his father, Chad, is the superintendent...Served as a Mormon missionary in Nenquen, Argentina, and is fluent in Spanish.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T31st in 2014 at the Bayview Place Island Savings Open presented by Times Colonist.
